Read (repeated) time-to-event simulation data files.

Source: R/read.TTE.sim.data.R
read.TTE.sim.data.Rd

Read (repeated) time-to-event simulation data files.

Usage

read.TTE.sim.data(
  sim.file,
  subset = NULL,
  headers = c("REP", "ID", "DV", "TIME", "FLAG2", "DOSE"),
  xpose.table.file = FALSE,
  ...
)

Arguments

sim.file

Name of the simulated file.

subset

subset to extract.

headers

headers in file.

xpose.table.file

xpose table files.

...

Extra arguments passed to function.
